CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 21, 1959, pg. A22, reads: "Meet Me at the Fair - Preparations for the coming St. Nicholas Day Fair are now in making. Marvine Miller, left: Zigrida Fridenbergs, center, and Anita Jones, right, display a few of the articles which will be on sale during the fair.  The fair will last three days, and will be held at the YWCA on Spahr St. in East Liberty. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Marvine Miller, Zigrida Fridenbergs, and Anita Jones standing behind table with paper tree, dolls, and basket for St. Nicholas Day Fair at East Liberty YWCA, another version
